## 3. 구체적인 개선 방안

### 개선 1: fetch join으로 N+1 해결 (가장 중요)

**파일 위치:** `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/follow/FollowRepository.kt`

```kotlin
// [AFTER] - fetch join + Projection으로 1쿼리 처리
interface FollowRepository : JpaRepository<FollowEntity, String> {

    @Query("""
        SELECT new com.maum.backend.dto.follow.FollowingProjection(
            f.followingId,
            u.nickname,
            u.profileImageUrl,
            p.imageUrl,
            CASE WHEN rf.id IS NOT NULL THEN true ELSE false END
        )
        FROM FollowEntity f
        JOIN UserEntity u ON u.id = f.followingId
        LEFT JOIN ProfileEntity p ON p.userId = f.followingId
        LEFT JOIN FollowEntity rf ON rf.followerId = f.followingId AND rf.followingId = f.followerId
        WHERE f.followerId = :userId
        ORDER BY f.createdAt DESC
    """)
    fun findFollowingListWithDetails(userId: String): List<FollowingProjection>
}
```

**파일 위치:** `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/dto/follow/FollowingProjection.kt`

```kotlin
